I like this question, and I've got something that works, but I'm not sure it's the prefered solution.<p><pre><code>  function say(arg) {
    return function(word) {
      alert(arg + " " + word);
    };
  }
</code></pre>
It solves "hello world", but wouldn't work for something like say("dogs")("and")("cats"). Are you expecting an arbitrary number of function returns?
